  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n  \nEach tab_strip has a |contents_data_|[1] vector to store the WebContentsData of each tab.  \nWe now have 6 tabs from 0 to 5 and group them:  \nGroup_A : 0,1  \nGroup_B : 2,3,4,5  \n  \nThe |contents_data_| is as follows:  \ncontents_data_[0]->groupId = D03012E9FB65AC8D2ED44"
